Package: bigmemory
Version: 4.0
Date: 2009-10-07
Title: Manage massive matrices with support for shared memory and memory-mapped files.
Author: Michael J. Kane <kaneplusplus@gmail.com> and John W. Emerson <jayemerson@gmail.com>
Maintainer: John W. Emerson <john.emerson@yale.edu>
Depends: methods, utils
Description: Create, store, access, and manipulate massive matrices.  Matrices may
  optionally be allocated to shared memory and/or may use memory-mapped files.  Packages
  biganalytics, synchronicity, and bigalgebra provide advanced functionality.
License: LGPL-3
Copyright: (C) 2009 John W. Emerson and Michael J. Kane
URL: http://www.bigmemory.org
LazyLoad: yes
